{"h508629d7gba60g477bg9689g6a79d05eea5f": ["Mol says we can't talk to you any more. Um. Sorry. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "a7db10a3-22d7-d131-35c1-c0eb027ad172"], "hc1e6198aga72cg4c8agb428g89d59fa27440": ["I can't talk right now. I'm supposed to be looking for, um, marks. You know. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "fea3b02d-9dfb-90b6-e936-519df7ba260b"], "he2659214g471dg4ce6gbf44gcfc59aa27fec": ["No! Don't shake me again!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "d7fdde57-4f34-d20d-0719-d584a7de3508"], "h8e96ba65gdd12g49adga405g312713059bed": ["Mol! Help!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "5566416d-4e27-470d-e9e0-7361063221e3"], "h8a6cd05eg08a8g40dfg9e3egcc2e263f87d3": ["Oh. Hello again. Um.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "85c4d1a9-d05a-896a-f5ec-5299fb16a125"], "ha446942ag6a71g4c69gb338g3c45c144bcad": ["Mol's in charge here. Not me. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "acb67642-c353-bcdd-8de5-77b28890b1da"], "h6b36a6c2g82d8g4221gaba5ge0c38918023a": ["Oh. Hello again. Um.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "29e7057a-0fc9-7859-583f-8613d203ee49"], "hf54c815ag0895g4fadg8099g92ef68b30ba0": ["Oh. Um. Hi.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "0db5a91c-b62d-6d5c-db13-8738ea7b95ea"], "h02b520d6gad4cg48cegb19cg360e691c9631": ["I don't have money or anything to sell. My p-partner does that.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "15b57e38-bc53-6589-99d6-06514f214b8d"], "h2b8b3746g18c6g4905g960fg778d6a7d68b4": ["Is he your partner or your brother?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "263326e2-aec4-fc83-6adb-c40b61a81c48"], "h137af0c5g179bg4a85g85a8gb7de93ab3b83": ["Um. Both. Of course. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "8d8f9cf5-8fe5-56b4-890a-310640459ca3"], "h3a41999ege36ag4c65gbf7aga1794ac5a41e": ["It's a family business. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "5f1509bc-db23-283c-c24c-5915beb7dc1d"], "hc72f5fefg0633g4663gbb71g2bb3cc6de3ce": ["He sells the stuff and I... don't sell the stuff.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "59ea5c26-df95-a265-f75b-bc92e7216b25"], "hc2bf3e73g8975g4ab9gb166gd95a1aea7aca": ["You're just here to stand guard, then?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "80c0fa9b-2206-5c6f-2a8d-45de24fe3a8c"], "h4e1720cagcfe6g486bg8c1bg08ece1bbebfd": ["Right. So... look out! I'm watching you!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "59c00924-2529-fbd4-9c1c-77fe1bc4b6e6"], "h9b89adc7ge01ag4654g93e4g5e183559a4da": ["You sound pretty useless. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "28339b52-0078-a948-8b29-53c0c2545987"], "hd621c756gae08g4214g93cdgd08e9e12707a": ["<i>Leave</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "cecf97b6-d0d3-640b-c1fa-393449032155"], "h76dcb10cgd1d3g4feag92afgcdd9c49d74e3": ["So what's your side of the business?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "5455f153-b72b-2507-5f4d-715459489373"], "h2779f126g211bg4408gb7e0g2c131367a846": ["What? Um.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "f084d676-4203-3a82-4f03-6f9629df7d82"], "h4e02008ag3342g43cfg81d9g87407fd9b520": ["I'm the guard? So... don't steal anything! I'm watching you!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "f0cb3c43-ef52-d8f4-b1e8-3ddd123a8be5"], "h690a1d85g84ddg4b33gae9bgbe712ef6bdf1": ["Mol told me everything. Keep your hands to yourself. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "0ae2285f-77ae-1d04-0bf3-524edb2ed671"], "h9654a7aeg8338g4098g8464geae67aed3373": ["Um.  Sorry. Um. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "e4919e04-b2ee-7add-4140-083e5ab743fd"], "hc0248904gf763g4d2dgac19gd8cb54ee8f74": ["I will. Did I say sorry? Sorry. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "968bb019-747d-16e0-2186-91e0849632a7"], "h08ba24eeg4db4g4e27gb4c5ge4010f615d60": ["<i>Perform Mol's hand signal.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "07296038-f315-d3cb-6ca0-b567616bc460"], "h6ad7191bg5813g4845gac23g0358711e8529": ["<i>Leave</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "345cdcdc-e47f-a91c-db6f-a3d6ff1bee55"], "h5dcad059gf7e9g4945gb12dgd5e27741972e": ["Um. Hello again. Um. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "081d9f50-8364-c4c2-e543-7ca828635a53"], "h58a05bfbg2f50g4f33g8eeeg11f6692445c5": ["Oh. Hello again. Um.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "510c749d-91c1-0ef2-af59-0e345f78a51c"], "h2893f2afgc783g4791g8d1bgd0d4f627e84e": ["Oh. Hello again. Um.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "fcdd6204-4d7a-7ab0-0287-e725fbd40d56"], "h915053dfg3e75g42f2ga9fbgc0b782fe44ee": ["Um, hi. Are you here to see my brother?", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "849be1a8-7ef2-a387-7d12-c66919921fd1"], "h78fdd06cg2b37g41f6gb466g1c855c54750c": ["Um. My partner, I mean.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "0e1ed407-bd4d-6f99-b1da-da54655631f9"], "h66902866gdedfg431cgbf53g3f29f1bb4035": ["Oh. Um. You're back.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "78b34d0b-0f32-c4fa-b37a-a87d1bb0f50e"], "h554f7bd9g7236g4662g9ffcg75b701699325": ["Oh! Um. Hi? ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "d86562d4-6ad4-75fa-5a28-470132b6b0ab"], "h94556a94gf53eg43a3g9108g0a222b8746f2": ["<i>Leave</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "fc8b9a79-a7f0-bd70-62a4-0232c87612ed"], "h81f68a47g675dg4cebga7d9g82f41295e7c1": ["Oh! Um. Hi? ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "6b74ef84-2773-d974-8f0c-755bda4cf9d6"], "h13e6b82dg0b2bg4773g8818g82fdb12fa2be": ["Hello again! Um.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "c50d9728-f391-809c-7c60-c72b6fb1bc54"], "h70649cc9g7e23g46d1gae49ge68f9d77614f": ["Oh! Um. Hi? ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "e59da516-ef69-adf9-ed75-654fd0d47597"], "h8fcf7f0fgfe49g4427g9f8fgc6577ffc2575": ["I've been robbed. You're the guard - see anything suspicious?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "77af496f-978c-e2ca-13f9-186ca6be387a"], "h906b2a46g8384g4fcfg94adgb575ce019a27": ["Me? Suspicious? No?", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "a60d88ff-1480-9b86-b0d1-e099a5485c19"], "he846344cg944bg4a00g8e27g2712d444697d": ["Do you know of any thieves around here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "83956928-5883-c82a-6491-68ea28038733"], "h7e51e44cgbf1ag467cgb3f2gb7ac533d0d48": ["No. I sure don't.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "bddd9281-e1a7-85a7-b27a-40045a72b873"], "hc37eefc2g523cg4f9cgb0ecg377c1ff6d369": ["But, um, I'll go ask my boss for you. Right now. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "547f1e66-ed33-5500-d534-dbf008232a58"], "h0243f55eg86c7g492cga442g606010b4e101": ["Tell me the truth - or I'll feed you to a bear.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "aabb2200-3c92-f856-145f-22d903dbe29b"], "hb5036567g7c2eg4092g9402gf90fc24ccbbf": ["Nice try. The bears are nice here. Um. I think.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "bbe8e92b-3186-0520-6476-8589e2122c30"], "h7b73d0beg8558g4f1fgb0d5g9bdc842c559b": ["Are you sure about that?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "96daea47-0b2b-4aa4-3d16-b19dea162fd1"], "h1da06973gc6cfg4d93gaf27g9bd7521e2d11": ["Yes! Mol said they're calm as cats! She...", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "a8f9e7ad-fc54-876b-7d6f-3ebb139fce05"], "h4f2ac085gbafdg43f5ga098g255370d7647a": ["You know, you didn't deny lying to me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "f398ce8e-e1a1-5026-8c2f-935b2bae3607"], "h70ee1a75gfd0ag47c2g84c4gb98006dc51ed": ["What? N-no! We didn't do anything! Me and Mattis and Mol, we just...", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "ee61aa57-d33d-cd56-f16f-6f23d7bda385"], "h2ff85c63g0be7g40a3gb903gc46f981922e4": ["My teeth are sharper than any bear's, little one.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "8ca3e80f-2083-c623-da37-6714e476e5bb"], "hb6444854g2846g483bgb1b0g58c2b43ebfce": ["Y-you don't scare me. You won't do nothing with all the grown-ups around!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "3e87c0d3-86e4-3651-740c-39f5bab05258"], "h12a37395gc6fdg4f3egb86dgc197c966c275": ["Look at me. Do you really think it's the bears you have to worry about?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "892e10c1-e7ac-1be1-558e-79fefd4cc9c4"], "h29edea92gbf4dg434eg972bg1dcd4b140511": ["The bears might be. I'm not.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "0047cea5-728b-f27b-421f-41b549ae10c2"], "h3511b7acg74e3g41f4g9dd3gc2557e118ca5": ["Eep.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "b7ec3fa0-b74b-9319-0d5d-479a6877815a"], "hcf880f7agb7f7g4c8dg95ecg5fd6102f79b8": ["Stop... stop yelling at me! Or I'll call Mol!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "da80269b-04ef-4736-f792-c46a7a425bd4"], "h9e068719ge89cg4fc6ga897ga70b120028a1": ["Is Mol the one who stole from me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "7671fb37-5d3e-fd92-1aad-9d4a1c196621"], "hb0d9e9e3g94dcg4a18g9de1g2f43d5ea9c84": ["What? N-no! It wasn't her!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "1ba9ef79-6f98-8241-d82a-4889f6811ae9"], "h6b689af2g9e4eg45ccg9b04g7286952bd3bb": ["She's my... um. My... boss?", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "ffb71ff0-91c4-44e0-7e7d-2ab21f7aa81d"], "h073f45b7gf2e3g4adbg918dgc803bf787ca9": ["I shouldn't have said that. I gotta go!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "09c2c1d5-d448-3f5f-d468-b279ec658369"], "hfce5a2a0g8feeg4a61ga3fegc5f104b4b253": ["Wow - you really showed that small defenceless child who's in charge.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "4e5150a0-8343-f4c0-9fe3-a7acbf6fba1e"], "h369005a6g989dg4f01gafe9g4581f1c7b1cb": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "eadc41d6-c720-874d-004c-31fc3a446db9"], "h4d2046e6g408cg4671ga136g402c90e85306": ["*Before you can say anything else, she sprints away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "58458b46-0f20-ab04-ac37-76623d8eb847"], "hb03127f7gc630g4cbcg8b6fgc09f5a3a3b43": ["*Before you can say anything else, she sprints away.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "9821e193-db19-60f7-0272-e6979735c523"], "h83e51220g865eg4c1eg9142g892c8958f073": ["Your little friend doesn't frighten me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "21ff8acb-eaee-3e4b-4468-91fd55ba1cb5"], "hd8c0a3cbgf72eg4f18gbf29g011d002e9e64": ["She should! Mol's tougher than anyone! She...", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "48bcaf2c-a879-60cf-b418-9bd3508dc770"], "h8e1e4507g2816g4935gb7b1gb2aa6a3a00d7": ["Um. I wasn't supposed to say her name. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "e4d74972-7ba2-d22c-737a-e276e711d82a"], "h8b586edbg9114g419egab07g233efe0378d6": ["Anyway, I won't say anything else. You can't make me. Even if you murder me!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "a771286f-066a-f447-a98e-d960ff1530bf"], "h35038490g12d0g4aaag96dagd116e5f09443": ["Good. Then I can toss both of you into the river.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "e06987b7-7c8d-6359-dfac-95a80cc4f443"], "h6dd1b1d8gc525g498eg8509g95fe9223ec39": ["Oh. Um. We can both swim.", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "f1e1be03-e276-1ced-3f02-7428eafef61e"], "h74218e89g63cag4117gbcb9gb9706409d59b": ["You can't yell without a tongue. They go well with a pinch of salt. Tasty.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "c48097ce-7ac4-6604-8658-b658d37ca576"], "h100d70e0g95e3g494fg8040g53079578e286": ["Y-you wouldn't do that! Not with all the grown-ups around!", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "f42bf996-a3f5-2e6a-5fa2-1dcba1a2e258"], "h4fd01136geab0g4a0cgbe3bg54ddc939e5bd": ["I can crush you with one hand.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "86a42aea-6a79-813d-4df3-4887ac84857c"], "h847ca0ecg9d3dg4477gac15g0fecaad8d68e": ["Did you know that I can smell when people are lying?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "285ced8a-5928-b3c8-e5e1-315d77b12388"], "h3bfdac7cg8ff0g4f54g839ag409fd1194c0f": ["I don't know what you mean. At all. ", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "f3e52a86-c6ab-9a09-0341-df2440d99007"], "h7706f05egd185g449aga679g0349dba77611": ["Child - I'm a visitor here. I deserve better than this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "220e2568-0cbe-540a-d628-efc9c536b597"], "h995708a7gd023g4fc0ga0eegf02efe219c52": ["It's... It's just so hard! We're on our own, and Mol said she'd help us. She...", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "016decac-9bf0-8698-b707-7c6864a35303"], "he036c8f6gecb7g4622g9baagc0154cad0b94": ["I know your game - and it's sloppy. Drop the act.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "fdd4a94e-e13b-57d7-f990-1ee5a300740f"], "hfe557cc7g80e8g4a28ga9d7g96ad7766dfe5": ["It wasn't my idea, it was Mol's! She...", "540ddc1f-42c6-4347-ba03-b3cf3d3942ab", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "bee0fa9b-c5dd-f853-6619-082d8f3767c7"], "he0795c03g05aeg4da4ga36bgccbfee36fc27": ["I've been robbed. Have you seen anyone acting suspiciously?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Thieflings_Pickpocket_002.html", "110f2205-e57e-02cb-74a9-10296bb250b2"]}